{"article_id":"wwwnZXo8KLPzUnCz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"Michael Cohen 's quest for redemption drew Americans into the mob-like world of Donald Trump .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"The President 's former personal lawyer has painted a cruel and unseemly picture ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"shocking even with the nation 's senses dulled by years of Trump-induced controversy .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"In a theatrical day of congressional testimony Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"that will become an iconic moment of Trump 's presidency ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"Cohen","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"--","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"who is about to go to prison --","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"turned on his ex-client with the world watching .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"He made a case","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"after spending a decade inside Trump 's world ,","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"he knew the President better than anyone --","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"seeking to provide context for the flurry of investigations and claims of crimes and wrongdoing","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"surrounding the President .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"He sketched a stunning portrait of Trump 's organization and conduct in what turned into an extraordinary and unprecedented daylong indictment of the character of a sitting President .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"It was either the betrayal of a proven liar","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"who is making up tales","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"to save himself","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"or the courageous act of an unlikely hero","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"rising above his dirty past","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"to provide a national service ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"depending on which side of the committee room lawmakers sat on .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"According to Cohen ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Trump 's empire was awash in activity","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that needed a fixer .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Cohen told the House Oversight Committee","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"that he now bitterly regrets","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"he blindly took that role ,","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"which will ultimately deprive him of his freedom .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"`` My loyalty to Mr. Trump has cost me everything , ''","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Cohen said , in an apparent message to a former patron","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"who was likely watching on the other side of the planet , during his visit to Hanoi , Vietnam .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"Trump , for his part , answered a single question about Cohen after his summit with North Korean dictator Kim Jong Un ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"by slamming Democrats","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"for holding a hearing","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"and calling his former fixer a liar .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"`` He lied a lot , ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Trump said .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"`` He lied about so many different things . ''","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"In Trump 's world , the boss knew everything","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"that went on ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"according to Cohen .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Henchmen like Cohen came to know by osmosis what the big man wanted .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"His currency was threats .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"And bad tabloid news stories were bought up","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"-- even if they were n't true --","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"to stop them from sullying Trump 's personal image .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"There was one law of the Trump jungle","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"that everyone came to understand ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"including Cohen , in his years as the right hand of the titan of Trump Tower .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"`` Everybody 's job at the Trump Organization is to protect Mr. Trump , ''","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Wednesday 's hearing ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"which played out amid fiercely partisan scenes ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"contained revelations","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"that hinted at future and deeper legal exposure for the President .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Most notably , Cohen produced a personal check for $ 35,000","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that Trump signed while in office","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that appears to show","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"that the President reimbursed him for hush payments","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"he made to women","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"who claimed affairs with the then-GOP nominee .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Cohen has already admitted paying off the women in an infringement of campaign finance law .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"If it is proved that Trump","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"-- who has denied having affairs with the women --","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"knew","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"he was breaking the law ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"the President could be in serious trouble ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"even after he leaves office .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Cohen , a former confidant turned accuser , also revealed","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that prosecutors in New York were probing Trump 's organization for alleged illegality in a previously unpublicized case ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"underscoring the potential","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"that the biggest threat to the President may come not from special counsel Robert Mueller","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"but from the hard-charging US Attorney 's Office for the Southern District of New York .","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"it 's ominous news for the President , ''","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"said former southern district prosecutor Elie Honig on CNN .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Cohen also claimed","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"that he had overheard a call","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"in which Trump 's longtime political adviser Roger Stone told the then-GOP nominee in 2016","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"that WikiLeaks was due to dump a new trove of emails","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"that would be damaging to Hillary Clinton .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"And he said","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Trump knew in advance about a 2016 meeting between a Russian lawyer and his campaign team","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"designed to deliver `` dirt '' on Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Since Trump previously told Mueller in sworn written answers","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that neither of those statements were true ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"he could be in legal and political jeopardy","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"if Cohen or prosecutors can provide corroboration of Cohen 's claims .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Cohen 's appearance offered a window into parts of the Russia investigation","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"that the buttoned-down special counsel investigation has yet to provide .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"But the testimony also cast doubt on some reports","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"that had suggested vulnerability for Trump .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"For instance , Cohen testified","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"that he had never been to the Czech Republic ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"potentially knocking down one of the accusations in the Steele dossier , a document of raw intelligence leads","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that purported to show","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"that Trump was compromised by Russia .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"He also said","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"he did not believe","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"a rumored videotape","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"of Trump","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"striking his wife , Melania , in an elevator","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"existed .","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"And he said","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"that in any case , the President would never do such a thing .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"Cohen may have tarnished his own credibility","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"when he insisted","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"he never wanted a job in the Trump White House .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Multiple reports by CNN and other media suggest","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"that he was not telling the truth .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"`` I see a guy","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"who worked for 10 years","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"is here","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"trashing the guy","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"he worked for 10 years ,","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"did n't get a job in the White House ,","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"and now you 're behaving just like everyone else","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"who 's got fired","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"or did n't get the job","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"they wanted , ''","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"Rep. Jim Jordan , an Ohio Republican","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"who 's a key Trump ally ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"told Cohen .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"It was not immediately clear if Cohen 's day in the spotlight would bolster the arguments of Democrats","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"who already favor impeachment ,","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"since he did not have smoking gun evidence of collusion between Trump aides and Russia .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"`` House Democrats and Michael Cohen put on a circus","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"that was full of lies and uncorroborated allegations , ''","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"said Republican National Committee Chairwoman Ronna McDaniel .","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":133,"text":"Cohen :","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"Lying to first lady is one of my biggest regrets","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"Cohen :","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"Lying to first lady is one of my biggest regrets","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"00:49","depth":6},{"id":140,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"if Cohen is to be believed ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"thuggish , corrupt and even immoral behavior was endemic in Trump 's inner circle before and during his run for president in 2016 .","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"`` I am ashamed","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"because I know what Mr. Trump is .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"He is a racist .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"He is a conman .","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"He is a cheat , ''","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"Cohen said in his opening statement .","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"In a startling exchange with Democratic Rep. Jackie Speier of California , Cohen said","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"he had been directed by Trump to threaten people probably 500 times .","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"According to his testimony ,","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"lying came as easily as breathing .","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"`` Every day , most of us in the room coming in ...","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"we were going to lie for him on something .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"And that became the norm ,","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"and that is exactly what is happening now in this country , ''","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"Complaining that Trump now calls him a `` rat , ''","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"Cohen described an atmosphere of oppressive malice","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"in which Trump 's instructions were so obvious","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"that they did not need to be spelled out .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"`` He does n't tell you what he wants , ''","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"Cohen said ,","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"when asked whether Trump had coached him to lie to Congress in a previous appearance , one of the offenses","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"for which he will begin a three-year jail term in May .","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"`` I know what he means","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"because I have been around him for so long , ''","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"said Cohen ,","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"Trump created a `` party line ''","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"that everyone around him must reject any accusations of collusion with Russia .","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"He also said","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"the President 's lawyers had reviewed and edited the testimony at issue","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"-- another serious charge .","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"Democratic Rep. Gerry Connolly of Virginia became the latest Washington figure","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"to reach for a Mafia comparison","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"when describing the events in Trump 's inner circle ,","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"defending Cohen from GOP attacks .","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"`` This Congress historically has relied on all kinds of shady figures","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"who have turned , ''","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"Connolly said .","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"`` One of the most famous led to the decapitation of organized crime families in America :","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"Joe Valachi . ''","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"`` He was a witness ,","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"and he committed a lot worse crimes","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"than you are convicted of , ''","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"said Connolly ,","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"pointing directly at Cohen","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"while referencing 1960s congressional hearings","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"that lifted the lid on Mafia activities .","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":3},{"id":192,"text":"Preet Bharara :","depth":4},{"id":193,"text":"This is an ominous sign for Trump","depth":4},{"id":194,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":4},{"id":195,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":6},{"id":196,"text":"Preet Bharara :","depth":7},{"id":197,"text":"This is an ominous sign for Trump","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"01:14","depth":5},{"id":199,"text":"Preet Bharara , a former US attorney for the Southern District of New York","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"who 's a CNN senior legal analyst ,","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":202,"text":"the accounts of Trump 's apparently veiled instructions to Cohen were `` the kind of thing","depth":8},{"id":203,"text":"you see in mob cases . ''","depth":8},{"id":204,"text":"`` It 's the kind of thing","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"you see in environments","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"in which people do bad things","depth":12},{"id":207,"text":"but they do n't want to be on the hook and on the record","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"as asking someone to do a bad thing .","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"It happens all the time , ''","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"Bharara said on CNN 's `` The Situation Room . ''","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"Cohen also testified","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"that everything came from the top in the Trump Organization ,","depth":11},{"id":213,"text":"when he claimed","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"that the President had long inflated or deflated his company 's assets","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"-- for example , to make extravagant claims about his wealth ,","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"to get bank loans or in insurance claims .","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"`` Everything was done with the knowledge and at the direction of Mr. Trump , ''","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"His comment could undermine Trump 's denials","depth":9},{"id":220,"text":"that he had known anything about the many meetings between his aides and Russians .","depth":9},{"id":221,"text":"Since Cohen has likely told everything and more","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"that he said Wednesday to Mueller and other prosecutors","depth":10},{"id":223,"text":"with whom he has been cooperating ,","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"Trump 's exposure could be acute .","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"And claims by Republicans","depth":8},{"id":226,"text":"that Cohen can not be trusted","depth":8},{"id":227,"text":"were partially undermined by the fact","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"if he is proved to have lied in Wednesday 's hearing ,","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"he risks having time added to his sentence .","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"After the hearing , a tired Oversight Chairman Elijah Cummings delivered a verdict","depth":6},{"id":232,"text":"that may augur a fateful moment in American history","depth":6},{"id":233,"text":"when he was asked","depth":6},{"id":234,"text":"whether Trump may have committed a crime in office .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":469,"left":425,"right":468,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":425,"left":366,"right":424,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":366,"left":288,"right":365,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":0,"right":287,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":237,"right":286,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":1,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":256,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":248,"right":255,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":242,"right":247,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":238,"right":241,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":238,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":240,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":240,"left":6,"right":239,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par